law.history: Repealed 1984 Ky. Acts ch. 184, sec. 1, effective July 13, 1984; amended 1984 Ky. Acts ch. 123, sec. 2. -- Created 1980 Ky. Acts ch. 280, sec. 37.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Specified persons to report child abuse and neglect - Contents of report - Search warrant - Protective custody - Immunity from liability.
metadata.note: This section would have become effective July 15, 1984, but was, instead, repealed by 1984 Ky. Acts ch. 184, sec. 1, effective July 13, 1984.
